we must take before...

396
00:27:02,270 --> 00:27:03,150
I can...

397
00:27:05,580 --> 00:27:08,300
give up on everything
and leave tomorrow if I must.

398
00:27:08,960 --> 00:27:10,600
But I can't.

399
00:27:10,690 --> 00:27:13,140
No, I won't.

400
00:27:13,890 --> 00:27:15,260
I'm sure you all are aware

401
00:27:15,960 --> 00:27:18,770
of love and passion I put into Fantasia

402
00:27:18,860 --> 00:27:20,180
for the last three years.

403
00:27:21,550 --> 00:27:22,910
