404
00:27:23,610 --> 00:27:25,380
because of my love for Yeon-seo.

405
00:27:25,910 --> 00:27:28,640
I wanted to give back
a solid ballet theatre

406
00:27:28,730 --> 00:27:31,710
when my niece returns as a healthy woman.

407
00:27:31,800 --> 00:27:33,420
But Yeon-seo is not healthy

408
00:27:33,520 --> 00:27:34,920
