421
00:28:14,090 --> 00:28:17,340
We break up in teams, put on performances,
hold a party, and greet people too.

422
00:28:17,430 --> 00:28:19,050
-You know, don't you?
-I do.

423
00:28:19,140 --> 00:28:21,250
But you usually do it
at the end of the year,

424
00:28:21,340 --> 00:28:23,020
after you're done with big performances.

425
00:28:23,110 --> 00:28:24,770
Because you and Yeon-seo

426
00:28:24,860 --> 00:28:27,070
wreaked havoc on the ballet theatre,

427
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:29,180
