and come.

429
00:28:32,780 --> 00:28:34,900
-Yeon-seo too?
-She's the owner here.

430
00:28:34,980 --> 00:28:36,660
Of course, she should welcome her guests.

431
00:28:36,920 --> 00:28:40,520
