536
00:36:48,120 --> 00:36:51,080
Perfect. A man in this robe
is an expert at listening.

537
00:36:51,160 --> 00:36:52,170
Go ahead.

538
00:36:53,190 --> 00:36:54,240
Here?

539
00:36:54,730 --> 00:36:56,480
Have you ever kissed a human?

540
00:37:00,670 --> 00:37:01,680
